tyle below to expand it.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/9/E9BC83C4A7082FEF446BA7AEE2CB8F92.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style FJ</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9-?&quot; x 11-½&quot; File Jacket Folder</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/0/40EF0C59EC293B20F7B74B233E3042B4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style A</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9&quot; x 12&quot; Standard Presentation Folder&lt;br&gt;\nOur most popular style layout and if no other layout style is selected we will produce your order with this style.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/3/9375805603E5E4975FB305B5D5799BE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style B</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9&quot; x 12&quot; One Pocket. Left side single pocket available upon request.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/C/3C0A29702F55C9CE10EBB78B81CA22B9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border bor