-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style N3</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9-1/2&quot; x 11-1/2&quot; Continuous Reinforced Pocket Folder</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/1/313F3922FE7B522C6E9282626C3F9D27.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style N4</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9&quot; x 12&quot; Folder with rounded corner pockets</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/D/BD733F8D54DFCD641B617D4092507115.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style N5</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9&quot; x 12&quot; Single vertical pocket folder. Holds a vertical business card.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/F/3F768AEBAD7EAE119BA2D55763DC057F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Folder Styles</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Style P</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">9&quot; x 12&quot; Reinforced Pocket Folder</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutr